			select.playerOption
				option(value='') Please Select
				each player, index in data.players
					option #{player} - #{data.numbers[index]}
		div.basket
				p All hero prints are Â£20.
		span.linkToCustom Can't find who you are looking for? 
			a(href="/heroOrCustom?strip=" + data.strip + "&club=" + data.club + "&printingType=custom&deliveryType=" + data.deliveryType +"&style=" + data.style + "&premOrDifferent=" + data.premOrDifferent  + "&childOrAdult=" + data.childOrAdult) Input them yourself.
